"/?pet=crackers\">Crackers</a> (Rogue)</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/?pet=hateful eye\">Hateful Eye</a> (Demon Hunter or Warlock)</li><li><a href=\"/?pet=snowfang\">Snowfang</a> (Shaman)</li><li><a href=\"/?pet=bloodbrood whelpling\">Bloodbrood Whelpling</a> (Death Knight)</li><li><a href=\"/?pet=frostbrood whelpling\">Frostbrood Whelpling</a> (Death Knight)</li><li><a href=\"/?pet=vilebrood whelpling\">Vilebrood Whelpling</a> (Death Knight)</li></ul>','Y','N','N',394,1,7,'Y',1731,2,6,'N',256,4,1,'Y',398,10,7,'Y',409,15,7,'Y',607,20,2,'Y',0,0,352,157,326,84,0,'2016-08-02 00:00:00',1,1,1,0,'',6,700030);
