endor:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.wowhead.com/npc=68363\" target=\"_blank\">Quackenbush</a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Zone:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"/wow-pets/map/tylarr-gronnden/stormwind_city/\" class=\"zonewithpets\">Stormwind City</a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Faction:</span>&nbsp;Brawler\'s Guild - Rank 3</p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Cost:</span>&nbsp;500<img src=\"/images/wow16/moneyframe/ui-goldicon.png\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" alt=\"gold\" title=\"gold\"/> (unlimited supply)</p>','Y','','To purchase this pet, players must first reach rank 3 with the Brawler\'s Guild faction. Ranks are gained by defeating waves of PVE challenges in an arena-type setting.\r\n<br><br>\r\nParticipation in the Brawler\'s Guild is by invite only.<br><br>\r\nThe price of this pet is affected by your standing (reputation) with Orgrimmar or Stormwind City.','Y','N','N',406,1,1,'Y',436,2,6,'N',762,4,1,'Y',532,10,1,'Y',221,15,1,'Y',1078,20,1,'N',0,0,386,113,359,70,0,'2017-01-10 00:00:00',1,1,1,0,'',6,701050);
INSERT INTO `pets_defs` VALUES (931,2018,118063,868,7,40,'N','',0,234556,'Paradox Spirit','paradox-spirit','Paradox Spirit','U','blue',50,3,5.066,'','P','Neutral','Timeless Isle','Ground','None','Idles about.','','N','','Y','N','N','N','N','N','N','N',0,'paradox-spirit.jpg','wow64/icons/inv/pet/pandarenelemental.png','wow64/icons/inv/pet/pandarenelemental.png','','','It is a riddle wrapped in a mystery inside an enigma.','|cFFFFD200Vendor: |rMistweaver Xia|n|cFFFFD200Zone: |rTimeless Isle|n|cFFFFD200Cost: |r2200|Hcurrency:1166|h|TInterface\\Icons\\pvecurrency-justice.BLP:0|t|h','remove	2	\nadd	2	Cost: 2200|TINTERFACE\\ICONS\\pvecurrency-justice.BLP:0|t\nappend	2	(unlimited supply)\nadd	0	World Event: Mists of Pandaria Timewalking\nlink	Mistweaver Xia	http://ptr.wowhead.com/npc=118828/mistweaver-xia\nzones	Timeless Isle	Timeless Isle','<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">World Event:</span>&nbsp;Mists of Pandaria Timewalking</p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Vendor:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://ptr.wowhead.com/npc=118828/mistweaver-xia\" target=\"_blank\">Mistweaver Xia</a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Zone:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"/wow-pets/map/paradox-spirit/timeless_isle/\" class=\"zonewithpets\">Timeless Isle</a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Cost:</span>&nbsp;2200<a href=\"http://www.wowhead.com/currency=1166\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/images/wow16/icons/pvecurrency-justice.png\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" alt=\"Timewarped Badge\" title=\"Timewarped Badge\"/></a> (unlimited supply)</p>','N','','This pet is available for purchase during the Mists of Pandaria Timewalking Bonus Event.','Y','N','N',118,1,9,'Y',123,2,9,'N',1810,4,6,'N',419,10,9,'Y',405,15,7,'Y',456,20,6,'Y',0,0,422,116,380,66,0,'2017-01-10 00:00:00',1,1,1,0,'',6,701050);
INSERT INTO `pets_defs` VALUES (932,2004,117371,706,5,32,'N','',0,233805,'Trashy','trashy','Trashy','U','blue',50,3,6.3178,'rep / fish','P','Neutral','black raccoon, racoon, fishing, Dalaran (Broken Isles)','Ground','Pit-pattering footsteps; vocalizations (on-click)','Looks around. Occasionally sits down and defecates.','','N','','Y','N','N','N','N','N','N','N',0,'trashy.jpg','wow64/icons/inv/pet/raccoon.png','wow64/icons/inv/pet/raccoon.png','','Right Click to summon and dismiss Trashy.','How do you kill that which lives in garbage?','|cFFFFD200Vendor: |rConjuror Margoss|n|cFFFFD200Zone: |rDalaran|n|cFFFFD200Faction: |rConjuror Margoss - Best Friend|n|cFFFFD200Cost: |r50|TINTERFACE\\ICONS\\INV_ELEMENTAL_MOTE_WATER01:0|t','add	0	Profession: Fishing\nappend	1	- Best Friend\nremove	3	\nremove	3	\nadd	3	Cost: 50|TInterface\\ICONS\\inv_elemental_primal_water.blp:0|t\nappend	3	(unlimited supply)\ninline	Dalaran	Dalaran (Broken Isles)\nlink	Conjurer Margoss	http://legion.wowhead.com/faction=1975/conjurer-margoss\nzones	Dalaran (Broken Isles)	Dalaran (Broken Isles)','<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Profession:</span>&nbsp;Fishing</p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Vendor:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://legion.wowhead.com/faction=1975/conjurer-margoss\" target=\"_blank\">Conjurer Margoss</a> - Best Friend</p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Zone:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"/wow-pets/map/trashy/dalaran_broken_isles_/\" class=\"zonewithpets\">Dalaran (Broken Isles)</a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FFD200;\">Cost:</span>&nbsp;50<a href=\"http://legion.wowhead.com/item=138777/drowned-mana\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/images/wow16/icons/inv/elemental/primal_water.png\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" alt=\"Drowned Mana\" title=\"Drowned Mana\"/></a> (unlimited supply)</p>','Y','','This pet can be purchased from Conjurer Margoss in Dalaran (Broken Isles). Players must have the Best Friend reputation with Conjurer Margoss in order to buy Trashy.<br><br>\r\nConjurer Margoss\' location can be accessed by using <a href=\"http://legion.wowhead.com/item=138448/emblem-of-margoss\" target=\"_blank\">Emblem of Margoss</a>. This item that can be fished up from green pools in Dalaran\'s Underbelly. Using this item will teleport the player to Margoss - he can be found next to a pond on one of Dalaran\'s floating islands.<br><br>Alternatively, players can glide or slow fall from the Pet Battle area in Dalaran to Margoss\' location. <br><br>\r\nUpon first meeting Conjurer Margoss, he will have a quest for the player to fish up <a href=\"http://legion.wowhead.com/item=138777/drowned-mana\" target=\"_blank\">Drowned Mana</a> from the nearby pond. Completing this quest will reward 250 friendship.<br><br>\r\nDrowned Mana is not only the currency used to purchase Trashy, but can also be turned in to Margoss in exchange for friendship. Each Drowned Mana yields 50 reputation.<br><br>\r\nOccasionally players may fish up <a href=\"http://legion.wowhead.com/item=141975/mark-of-aquaos\" target=\"_blank\">Mark of Aquaos</a>. Using this item will spawn a hostile creature, Aquaos. Killing him will turn the small pond into a temporary source of increased Drowned Mana, where successful casts are guaranteed to yield Drowned Mana and sometimes multiple Mana.','Y','N','Y',1796,1,5,'Y',566,2,5,'Y',568,4,8,'N',152,10,8,'Y',158,15,1,'Y',1797,20,5,'Y',0,0,361,102,346,60,0,'2017-01-10 00:00:00',1,1,1,0,'',6,701050);
