.com/order-advancement=545\" taget=\"_blank\">Fortuitous</a>. This talent increases the chance to loot Sands of Time from mobs within the scenario by 100%, increasing the odds of receiving Time-Lost Wallets.','Y','Y','N',122,1,2,'Y',1934,2,2,'N',600,4,6,'N',588,10,2,'Y',611,15,2,'N',1933,20,6,'N',0,0,390,343,340,215,0,'2017-06-13 16:06:41',1,1,1,0,'',6,702050);
